Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.40,0:00:10.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}歡迎光臨 歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.74,0:00:13.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}超准的占卜不來看看嗎
