Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.84,0:01:55.67,title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(888,609)}{\fad(300,300)}第 9 話  『 必定改變未來』
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.88,0:02:00.89,*Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.13,0:01:55.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}占卜？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.05,0:02:00.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}還順便賣炒麵麵包 形跡可疑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.05,0:02:02.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}要試試嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.76,0:02:04.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}潮君 你先來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.85,0:02:08.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}歡迎來到占卜屋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.69,0:02:11.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}搞什麼 這不是山田嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.69,0:02:13.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}在下並非山田
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.52,0:02:14.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}在下的名字是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.57,0:02:19.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}宇宙的預言者龍田山
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.16,0:02:20.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}就是山田吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.49,0:02:22.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}請叫在下田山
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.74,0:02:26.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那麼現在就開始預知你的未來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.91,0:02:28.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}請先閉上眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.62,0:02:30.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}準備好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.13,0:02:35.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我數到三 不能睜眼哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.76,0:02:37.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}三 二
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.13,0:02:42.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你你你你在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.93,0:02:44.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.51,0:02:46.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你剛親我了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.89,0:02:49.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我看見了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.35,0:02:53.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你和小田切寧寧在間接接吻
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.02,0:02:54.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}就這些了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.52,0:02:56.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.90,0:03:00.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}在使用猿島的未來預知能力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.49,0:03:02.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}山田的炒麵麵包賣不出去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.53,0:03:03.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}這是無奈之舉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.03,0:03:05.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不過想法是我提的就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.24,0:03:07.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我們走吧潮君
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.83,0:03:08.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}已經可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.12,0:03:10.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}喂 這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.66,0:03:12.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我已經不要了給你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.92,0:03:15.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}間接接吻
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.96,0:03:17.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}下一個
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.13,0:03:20.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}現在等候時間是40分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.76,0:03:22.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}排好隊 請排好隊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.76,0:03:24.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}要保持好隊形哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.80,0:03:28.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}太好了 我的能力用上了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.06,0:03:32.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}託你的福炒麵麵包都賣光了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.69,0:03:36.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}這樣算是稍微能還你火災時的恩情了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.82,0:03:40.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}沒什麼的 那件事也不至於還要你報答
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.20,0:03:42.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.40,0:03:43.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.07,0:03:48.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那麼山田君 我有些事想找你商量
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.83,0:03:54.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那個 能夠把我魔女的能力抹消嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.46,0:03:56.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.13,0:04:03.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我想談戀愛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.22,0:04:07.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}一接吻就能看見未來什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.60,0:04:09.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}就不能和喜歡的人交往了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.60,0:04:14.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.19,0:04:24.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是你吧 叫玉木真一的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.91,0:04:29.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}喂 聽到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.62,0:04:34.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}又有囉嗦的笨蛋跑來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.67,0:04:35.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.67,0:04:38.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}找我什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.71,0:04:41.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是有點突然 但是我有一個請求
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.51,0:04:45.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}有個魔女希望你能幫她消除能力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.93,0:04:49.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你到底在說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.35,0:04:50.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}裝傻也沒用
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.60,0:04:54.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}為什麼你知道呢 我的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.06,0:04:57.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我可是有特別的情報網的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.31,0:05:00.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}大概也就是瀧川諾亞那傢伙了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.48,0:05:02.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}真麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.61,0:05:06.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}話說從剛才開始你內心的吐槽 都不小心說出來了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.62,0:05:09.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}看來也找不到什麼藉口了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.03,0:05:11.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那你跟我來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.83,0:05:17.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}就如你所知我的能力就是奪取魔女的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.38,0:05:25.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}也就是說我現在就擁有從某個魔女那奪來的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.72,0:05:27.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}原來如此啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.43,0:05:29.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我現在就讓你看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.97,0:05:32.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}啊 真麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.72,0:05:34.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}都說了 你的內心都聽到了喂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.69,0:05:39.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}喂 你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.78,0:05:46.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.12,0:05:54.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不是我…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.54,0:05:56.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}騙子！變態！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.37,0:05:58.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}太差勁了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.79,0:06:00.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}知道了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.67,0:06:06.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我所有的能力是讓接吻的對象看不見我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.13,0:06:09.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}就是變成透明人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.34,0:06:10.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}真厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.39,0:06:11.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.05,0:06:14.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}如果和其他的魔女接吻的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.81,0:06:17.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}這個能力會被替換而消失
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.81,0:06:20.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}所以我不能答應你的請求
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.27,0:06:21.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}抱歉啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.73,0:06:26.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}等一下 我也不可能就這麼回去的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.19,0:06:29.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}真是吵死了 既然如此的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.29,0:06:38.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}拜拜 山田君
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.54,0:06:41.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}這樣在你面前我應該就消失了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.96,0:06:46.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我說了等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.63,0:06:50.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}為什麼你還看得見我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.80,0:06:51.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}誰知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.09,0:06:55.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}總之看起來你是逃不出我的手掌心了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.60,0:07:00.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}也就是說你也是類似的魔女殺手咯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.60,0:07:02.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}魔女…殺手？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.73,0:07:04.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.82,0:07:06.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}如果你能接受我的請求的話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.07,0:07:08.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我就回應你的請求
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.15,0:07:10.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}哈？為什麼是我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.28,0:07:12.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}交換條件啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.16,0:07:14.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}也可以說是交易
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.99,0:07:18.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我就暫時先聽聽好了 說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.20,0:07:23.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}其實我看中了下任學生會會長的席位
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.13,0:07:28.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我想讓你調查一下下屆會長的繼任者
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.88,0:07:30.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}繼任者？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.76,0:07:33.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}這種事你自己調查不就好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.64,0:07:35.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}這可是機密事項
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.89,0:07:38.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不是輕易就能知道的情報
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.10,0:07:41.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}山崎確實是守口如瓶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.77,0:07:44.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}如果你順利調查到了的話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.19,0:07:48.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我就幫你消除你那位魔女的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.79,0:07:58.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}山田君
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.91,0:08:01.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}您有什麼事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.46,0:08:07.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}要找會長的話 他在巡視文化祭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.13,0:08:10.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}馬上就會回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.71,0:08:11.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.93,0:08:16.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}久等了久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.14,0:08:18.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不好意思啊山田
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.43,0:08:21.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我有點玩過頭了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.52,0:08:24.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那麼你找我什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.56,0:08:28.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我有話想單獨和你說
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.24,0:08:33.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}啊 飛鳥的話沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.28,0:08:36.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}沒有作為秘書的她的話 我也當不了會長
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.95,0:08:40.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我們是無法分開的關係
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.12,0:08:45.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}還是說有女孩子在你會害羞嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.13,0:08:48.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不是 那我說了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.59,0:08:52.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你準備讓誰成為下屆學生會長
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.34,0:08:55.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}下屆的？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.18,0:08:59.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}對 除了宮村和小田切還有其他人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.72,0:09:00.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你決定是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.97,0:09:04.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}就算是山田你的請求 我也無法回答
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.90,0:09:08.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}就是說你不能告訴我咯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.56,0:09:09.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.52,0:09:10.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}可惡 果然是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.40,0:09:12.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}既然這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.03,0:09:18.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不要 我拒絕 把我的能力用在這種事情上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.20,0:09:20.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}話雖這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.54,0:09:24.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我也很在意會長的評價
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.66,0:09:25.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}也是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.71,0:09:29.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}既然猿島有麻煩的話 我也想幫她
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.50,0:09:30.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}好的 就這麼定了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.63,0:09:34.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}要上了 使用小田切的魅惑能力
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.51,0:09:35.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}看 UFO！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.72,0:09:44.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}會長 您沒受傷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.19,0:09:54.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.36,0:09:59.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那麼 你能告訴我為什麼你要和我接吻嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.91,0:10:02.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}這可不好辦了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.24,0:10:05.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}誰要管你幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.95,0:10:08.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不不 不是我 是山田你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.42,0:10:14.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}看吧 接下來真的要斷了喲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.09,0:10:18.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}有什麼關係 有一個想消除掉自己能力的魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.34,0:10:21.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}為了那個傢伙我需要情報啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.47,0:10:23.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}能力？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.68,0:10:26.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是的 我可不會放棄的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.02,0:10:28.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.27,0:10:33.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}如果是這件事的話我來幫你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.23,0:10:35.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.40,0:10:39.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是我請會長幫我消除的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.41,0:10:43.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}魔女的透明人的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.58,0:10:45.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}透明人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.20,0:10:49.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}也就是說玉木的能力是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.83,0:10:51.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是我擁有的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.42,0:10:55.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你也認識玉木嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.88,0:10:57.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}山田你真是讓人吃驚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.76,0:11:00.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你能告訴我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.97,0:11:02.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}就算是飛鳥的請求也不行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.72,0:11:06.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}因為還不能做決定
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.14,0:11:10.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}原本最有競爭力的是玉木
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.10,0:11:15.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但是由於這件事 我不得不重新考慮一下他的評價了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.19,0:11:19.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}也就是說三人的評價完全打平了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.99,0:11:21.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}這可麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.62,0:11:26.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}就算你這麼說這也不是能輕易決定的事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.87,0:11:29.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}對了 用比賽來決勝負吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.00,0:11:31.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你這不是輕易地決定了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.25,0:11:34.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你知道嗎 山田
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.75,0:11:39.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}在這個學校存在著七位魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.30,0:11:47.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}說是要找第七個魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.18,0:11:51.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}的確至今能確認的魔女有六位
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.94,0:11:54.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那你們兩個事怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.56,0:11:56.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}就是說不算男生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.11,0:12:01.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但是只要找到第七個人就能當下屆學生會長了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.07,0:12:03.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}還真是簡單明瞭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.24,0:12:06.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我們快開始尋找魔女吧 潮
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.78,0:12:07.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.95,0:12:09.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我們超研部也開始找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.95,0:12:14.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不 宮村當不當會長是你的事 跟我們沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.17,0:12:17.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但是玉木 你可要遵守約定啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.17,0:12:20.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}現在快把猿島的能力消除吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.92,0:12:22.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}現在還做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.88,0:12:23.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.30,0:12:28.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你想想 如果我奪取了猿島的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.85,0:12:31.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那我所有的透明人的能力就會消失
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.35,0:12:35.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}然後就會誕生新的擁有這個能力的魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.23,0:12:40.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}要是存在兩個迷之魔女遊戲就無法成立
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.49,0:12:42.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}也是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.94,0:12:46.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}別擔心啦 我一定會遵守約定的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.91,0:12:49.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但這是在找到最後一位魔女之後的事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.54,0:12:55.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}就是這樣 你再等等沒問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.63,0:12:59.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}沒問題 謝謝你告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.00,0:13:02.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你跟我接吻就又…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.51,0:13:03.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.34,0:13:04.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}啊什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.05,0:13:07.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我好像又看到什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.01,0:13:09.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}討厭 抱歉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.97,0:13:13.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}太棒了 山田 能力真的消失了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.81,0:13:14.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.69,0:13:17.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}謝謝你 玉木
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.65,0:13:20.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}沒什麼 這都是小事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.98,0:13:22.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}多虧了這個我才成為了學生會長
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.78,0:13:26.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}怎麼了 山田
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.32,0:13:28.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你看到了怎麼樣的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.12,0:13:32.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是你能力消失的未來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.08,0:13:37.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}再見 我要回活動室了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.62,0:13:38.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}OK see you
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.92,0:13:40.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}搞什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.96,0:13:46.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不好 是會議的時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.13,0:13:49.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}看 我的秘書來接我了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.72,0:13:55.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}怎麼了 山田 這麼慌張
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.44,0:13:58.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}宮村 我們馬上去找魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.48,0:14:03.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}怎麼了 跟剛才的態度完全不同
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.36,0:14:12.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}喂 山田 你看到了怎樣的未來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.78,0:14:15.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}沒 沒看到什麼未來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.91,0:14:20.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}撒謊 你見過猿島之後樣子就很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.21,0:14:23.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}說吧 不說的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.46,0:14:28.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我知道了 當上會長的是玉木
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.09,0:14:31.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}這算不上答案啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.18,0:14:35.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我想知道你決定幫助我的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.31,0:14:37.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你真正看到了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.27,0:14:43.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}白石成為了他的秘書
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.11,0:14:46.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}什麼啊 這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.53,0:14:48.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}學生會長的秘書什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.11,0:14:52.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不就是年級第一的優等生應有的地位嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.62,0:14:53.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不是這麼一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.37,0:14:55.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.20,0:14:58.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}還是說白石離開了我們
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.00,0:15:00.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}都說了不是了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.96,0:15:02.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}白石她…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.29,0:15:06.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}真抱歉 讓你特地來接我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.92,0:15:07.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.92,0:15:09.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}今天的議題是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.22,0:15:14.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是關於演藝部的預算申請和校內展示板的使用規則
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.18,0:15:17.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}喂 白石
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.57,0:15:33.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}看到她那種表情 我怎麼能坐視不管
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.37,0:15:36.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你…難道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.16,0:15:41.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是啊 我喜歡白石
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.48,0:16:05.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}這些是在學校內惹過事的學生名單
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.02,0:16:11.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不管魔女願意或是不願意 都很容易成為騷動的中心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.20,0:16:14.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}首先從這一點下手比較好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.95,0:16:18.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}昨天的後夜祭你們也沒來 還以為你們消失了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.45,0:16:22.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}玉木會長的未來有這麼不好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.87,0:16:27.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}等一下 我覺得可以先從這個名單上排除男生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.42,0:16:30.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}對啊 魔女應該是女生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.34,0:16:32.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不愧是白石
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.80,0:16:36.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}雖然我想這樣說 馬上開始調查吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.55,0:16:39.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但是在不知道她有什麼能力的情況下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.02,0:16:41.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}請大家謹慎行動
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.81,0:16:49.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}伊藤 椿
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.19,0:16:50.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.74,0:16:53.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}這次的會長選戰 請幫助我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.61,0:16:56.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}這不僅是為了我 也是為了山田
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.45,0:16:57.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.33,0:17:00.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.41,0:17:01.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}有點噁心的說
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.53,0:17:33.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.93,0:00:00.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.61,0:17:34.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}還是什麼都沒打聽出來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.99,0:17:36.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.20,0:17:37.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.12,0:17:39.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.33,0:17:42.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}山田找魔女有什麼理由嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.66,0:17:44.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}一定有的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.08,0:17:46.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}現在不說可以
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.71,0:17:50.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不過 到了可以說的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.59,0:17:51.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}要原原本本地告訴我哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.51,0:17:55.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.89,0:18:03.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你還真是悠閒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.64,0:18:08.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}還是說你已經放棄當會長了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.40,0:18:11.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我只是在等待時機而已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.86,0:18:16.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}真是不知道他在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.15,0:18:18.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}玉木已經沒有競爭力了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.91,0:18:21.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}現在就是你我二人的競爭了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.45,0:18:24.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你就好好加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.16,0:18:30.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那傢伙還真的特意去挖苦玉木
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.83,0:18:32.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}然後還向我匯報
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.29,0:18:34.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是太閒了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.92,0:18:39.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}反正我們也沒有把玉木放在眼裡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.51,0:18:43.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}嗯 我們的目標只是問題學生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.14,0:18:44.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你怎麼了 山田
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.02,0:18:49.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}玉木那傢伙 原來打的是那個算盤
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.73,0:18:51.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那個是哪個？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.57,0:18:54.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.44,0:18:57.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}果然沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.03,0:19:02.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你們真是太不小心了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.78,0:19:09.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}聽好了 你們三人都中了玉木透明人的計了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.66,0:19:10.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.87,0:19:13.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}與我最後接吻的是猿島
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.34,0:19:17.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}可是卻沒有看到你們的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.63,0:19:20.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}也就是說你們身上有其他人的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.10,0:19:29.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}難道說玉木那傢伙 潛入過社團活動室嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.89,0:19:30.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}有這個可能
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.23,0:19:34.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}居然想搶我們的功勞
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.65,0:19:38.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}既然這樣就趕緊解除掉 破壞那傢伙的奸計
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.32,0:19:41.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不 就這樣好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.49,0:19:43.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.66,0:19:48.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}用身體交換的能力 讓玉木的內心改變
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.04,0:19:53.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}好的 沒有人注意到我們
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.92,0:19:56.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}即使在社團活動室裡也可以交換的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.59,0:19:58.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不是 但是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.09,0:20:00.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那可是在大家的面前啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.84,0:20:02.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}快點交換吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.52,0:20:09.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}等 等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.81,0:20:11.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}在那之前我先確認一下…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.44,0:20:14.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你真的願意交換嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.31,0:20:16.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}願意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.40,0:20:19.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}什麼願意 一旦交換 直到未來改變
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.98,0:20:21.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}可是都換不回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.36,0:20:24.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}說不定要有兩三天
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.62,0:20:28.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你說的 我早就做好準備了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.83,0:20:30.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}說 說的也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.25,0:20:33.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}還有件事 關於我家…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.37,0:20:36.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}妹妹巽美和老媽會來纏著我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.25,0:20:38.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你適時敷衍或者無視掉就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.63,0:20:41.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}嗯 我應付的了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.38,0:20:42.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}還有壁櫥裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.97,0:20:44.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}有個寫著秘的盒子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.18,0:20:48.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}喂 山田同學 怎麼還不吻我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.39,0:20:53.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不 等下 我還有事要確認…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.86,0:21:04.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你做什麼 我還沒做好心理準備
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.11,0:21:06.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我們回部室吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.04,0:21:12.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}等下 白石
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.25,0:21:17.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}有件事現在要告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.09,0:21:21.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}其實…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.59,0:21:24.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我看到的未來…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.63,0:21:27.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不只是玉木會當上會長…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.34,0:21:31.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}還看到了你會成為玉木的秘書的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.60,0:21:34.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是嗎 那沒關係了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.64,0:21:39.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}秘書而已 用學習和社團以外的時間去做就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.36,0:21:41.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}才不是那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.28,0:21:44.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我看到 未來的你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.24,0:21:48.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是第一次和我交換身體時候的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.91,0:21:57.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我可是 再也不想看到你那種表情了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.67,0:22:05.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是嗎 是這麼回事嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.72,0:22:07.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不過你想多了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.22,0:22:13.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}因為我不打算再變回原來的自己了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.23,0:22:19.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}所以拜託了 一定要改變未來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.93,0:00:00.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.78,0:23:53.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}幫我占卜一下能不能交到朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.03,0:23:56.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那就讓龍田山幫你看一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.41,0:23:58.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}下集 山田君與七魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.54,0:23:59.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}請和我交往吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.91,0:24:01.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}影像太模糊了 什麼都看不清
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.96,0:24:03.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}簡直就像透明人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.93,0:00:00.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}
